nor-and-Eamonn-M.-McCormack-via-GETTY.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="莫比和本杰明·西番雅。图片来源：Kris Connor 和 Eamonn M. McCormack，来自 GETTY" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Moby-and-Benjamin-Zephaniah.-Credit-Kris-Connor-and-Eamonn-M.-McCormack-via-GETTY.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Moby-and-Benjamin-Zephaniah.-Credit-Kris-Connor-and-Eamonn-M.-McCormack-via-GETTY-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Moby-and-Benjamin-Zephaniah.-Credit-Kris-Connor-and-Eamonn-M.-McCormack-via-GETTY-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Moby-and-Benjamin-Zephaniah.-Credit-Kris-Connor-and-Eamonn-M.-McCormack-via-GETTY-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Moby-and-Benjamin-Zephaniah.-Credit-Kris-Connor-and-Eamonn-M.-McCormack-via-GETTY-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Moby-and-Benjamin-Zephaniah.-Credit-Kris-Connor-and-Eamonn-M.-McCormack-via-GETTY-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <a href="/artists/moby">Moby</a>分享了一首新歌“你的骄傲在哪里？”其中以<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/poet-benjamin-zephaniah-has-died-aged-65-3555288">已故诗人本杰明·西番雅</a>为主角。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/features/music-interviews/does-rock-n-roll-kill-braincells-moby-3393865">摇滚乐会杀死脑细胞吗？！ ——莫比</a></strong></li></ul><p>这位诗人、演员和政治活动家<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/poet-benjamin-zephaniah-has-died-aged-65-3555288">于 12 月去世，享年 65 岁</a>。他的去世消息是在他的 Instagram 页面上宣布的，八周前他被诊断出患有脑肿瘤。</p><p> “你的骄傲在哪里？”以西番雅 (Zephaniah) 的节奏节奏表演一首口语诗。 <em>“你的爱在哪里/你的信仰在哪里/你的希望在哪里/你的位置在哪里，</em> ”他以其特有的流畅风格背诵道。 </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="moby ft. Benjamin Zephaniah - “你的骄傲在哪里？” （官方音频）" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/npx6_S5uQX8?start=42&#038;feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p>莫比在一份声明中谈到这首歌（根据<a href="https://www.thelineofbestfit.com/news/moby-celebrates-the-late-benjamin-zephaniah-with-where-is-your-pride" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>《The Line Of Best Fit</em></a> 》）时说：“作为一名素食主义者，作为一个明智而富有同情心的人，本杰明多年来一直激励着我。我希望《你的骄傲在哪里》尊重他的遗产，也引起人们对他的生活、工作和原则的关注。”</p><p>这位电子音乐家兼制作人还在 Instagram 上分享了一段视频，透露他和 Zephaniah 原本打算去年发行这首歌曲，但这位诗人病重并不幸去世。</p><p> “我发布它是希望它能引起人们对本杰明的动物权利活动、他的博学、他诗意而美丽的精神和灵魂的关注。 “你的骄傲在哪里？”这是对本杰明的证明，也是对他的遗产的荣誉，”莫比在视频中说道。 </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/reel/C6_rYLSrwzy/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; width: 100px;"></div><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; width: 60px;"></div></div></div><div style="padding: 19% 0;"></div><div style="display:block; height:50px; margin:0 auto 12px; width:50px;"><svg width="50px" height="50px" viewBox="0 0 60 60" version="1.1" xmlns="https://www.w3.org/2000/svg" xmlns:xlink="https://www.w3.org/1999/xlink"><g stroke="none" stroke-width="1" fill="none" fill-rule="evenodd"><g transform="translate(-511.000000, -20.000000)" fill="#000000"><g><path d="M556.869,30.41 C554.814,30.41 553.148,32.076 553.148,34.131 C553.14